            <div class="faq-item bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:border-brand-blue/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
                <button class="faq-q w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 px-7 py-5 text-left"><span class="font-poppins font-bold text-navy text-sm">Apakah proses khitan terasa sakit?</span><div class="faq-icon w-8 h-8 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand-light text-brand-blue flex items-center justify-center text-xs"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div></button>
                <div class="faq-a px-7 pb-5 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Dengan anestesi topikal tanpa jarum suntik, rasa sakit sangat diminimalkan. Banyak anak hanya merasakan sedikit tekanan tanpa nyeri berarti. Dokter juga melakukan pendekatan emosional agar anak tetap tenang.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:border-brand-blue/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
                <button class="faq-q w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 px-7 py-5 text-left"><span class="font-poppins font-bold text-navy text-sm">Berapa lama durasi tindakan khitan?</span><div class="faq-icon w-8 h-8 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand-light text-brand-blue flex items-center justify-center text-xs"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div></button>
                <div class="faq-a px-7 pb-5 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Proses khitan berlangsung sekitar 10–20 menit. Termasuk persiapan dan pemeriksaan, total waktu sekitar 30–45 menit. Setiap tahapan dilakukan teliti dan aman.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:border-brand-blue/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
                <button class="faq-q w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 px-7 py-5 text-left"><span class="font-poppins font-bold text-navy text-sm">Usia minimal untuk khitan berapa tahun?</span><div class="faq-icon w-8 h-8 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand-light text-brand-blue flex items-center justify-center text-xs"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div></button>
                <div class="faq-a px-7 pb-5 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Khitan bisa dilakukan dari usia bayi hingga dewasa. Usia yang direkomendasikan adalah 5–12 tahun karena anak lebih kooperatif dan penyembuhan lebih optimal.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:border-brand-blue/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
                <button class="faq-q w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 px-7 py-5 text-left"><span class="font-poppins font-bold text-navy text-sm">Metode khitan apa yang digunakan?</span><div class="faq-icon w-8 h-8 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand-light text-brand-blue flex items-center justify-center text-xs"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div></button>
                <div class="faq-a px-7 pb-5 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Kami menggunakan metode <strong class="text-navy">alat cetak modern</strong> yang presisi dan terstandar. Hasilnya rapi, minim perdarahan, dan pemulihan lebih cepat. Anestesi menggunakan krim topikal tanpa jarum suntik.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:border-brand-blue/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
                <button class="faq-q w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 px-7 py-5 text-left"><span class="font-poppins font-bold text-navy text-sm">Apakah tersedia layanan homecare (ke rumah)?</span><div class="faq-icon w-8 h-8 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand-light text-brand-blue flex items-center justify-center text-xs"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div></button>
                <div class="faq-a px-7 pb-5 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Ya! Kami menyediakan layanan homecare langsung ke rumah Anda dengan peralatan steril lengkap. Memberikan kenyamanan dan privasi lebih bagi anak dan keluarga.</div>
